I wrote the below in the late spring of 2021.
Small Packages My wife, Britta, went to bed a few minutes before me, calling down, &lsquo;Good night!&rsquo; as I was locking the front door. Just before I called back, I thought I heard a stranger say, &lsquo;Good night.&rsquo;
I called, &lsquo;What did you say?&rsquo;
&lsquo;Nothing&mdash;did you say something?&rsquo;
Naturally, I went to bed thinking that there was a person in our house&mdash;friendly enough, it seemed&mdash;wishing us both a good night.
